<strong>Nome Alternativo:</strong> Astor<br />
<strong>Pais:</strong> <a href="{% link _pessoas/SchererNorbertoEdgar1914.md %}">Norberto Edgar Scherer (1914-1986)</a> e <a href="" class="underconstruction">Elvira Quinot</a><br />
